node.text: I wrote this song crying in my kitchen just as life started to fall apart a bit. Recorded the vocal there n then, and put it as an interlude on the EP. now..surprise! 🥸 could cry just thinking about you (Full Version) is out on all streaming platforms 💜 saddest song ever but we okay now. Sorta 🤣🤣🤣 Love you
Digital art collection called BL00M2021, just dropped on @niftygateway in collaboration with @jasonebeyer. Raising money for @glaad 😚 very excited about this. Cop one for the LGBTQs if you want
